+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+ Building in PARTIAL compliance with RFC 3501 security
+ requirements:
+ Compliant:
++ TLS/SSL encryption is supported
+ Non-compliant:
++ Unencrypted plaintext passwords are permitted
+
+ In order to rectify this problem, you MUST build with:
++ SSLTYPE=unix.nopwd
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
